  *   going to Amazon -  here<https://www.amazon.com/Smooth-River-Inspirati=
on-Exquisite-Terminal/dp/1737503409/ref=3Dsr_1_1?dchild=3D1&keywords=3Dthe+=
smooth+river&qid=3D1632996752&s=3Dbooks&sr=3D1-1>,
  *   going to Barnes and Noble - here<https://www.barnesandnoble.com/w/the=
-smooth-river-richard-cohen/1140158408?ean=3D9781737503408>, or
  *   or plugging in your zip code and finding your local bookstore here<ht=
tps://www.indiebound.org/book/9781737503408>.

If you like it, please consider writing a review on Amazon, which might als=
o help others.

Feel free to forward this as you choose.

Warm regards,

